{
  "video_id": "LH8MPbFoRjw",
  "title": "Timothy Bartik: The economic case for preschool",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13286.0,
      "end_time": 17774.0,
      "text": "In this talk today, I want to present a different idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17774.0,
      "end_time": 21995.0,
      "text": "for why investing in early childhood education"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21995.0,
      "end_time": 24694.0,
      "text": "makes sense as a public investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24694.0,
      "end_time": 26932.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a different idea, because usually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26932.0,
      "end_time": 28305.0,
      "text": "when people talk about early childhood programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28305.0,
      "end_time": 31646.0,
      "text": "they talk about all the wonderful benefits for participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31646.0,
      "end_time": 34928.0,
      "text": "in terms of former participants, in preschool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34928.0,
      "end_time": 37193.0,
      "text": "they have better K-12 test scores,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37193.0,
      "end_time": 39308.0,
      "text": "better adult earnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39308.0,
      "end_time": 41423.0,
      "text": "Now that&#39;s all very important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41423.0,
      "end_time": 45519.0,
      "text": "but what I want to talk about is what preschool does"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45519.0,
      "end_time": 47341.0,
      "text": "for state economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47341.0,
      "end_time": 50638.0,
      "text": "and for promoting state economic development."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50638.0,
      "end_time": 53931.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s actually crucial"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53931.0,
      "end_time": 57254.0,
      "text": "because if we&#39;re going to get increased investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57255.0,
      "end_time": 59598.0,
      "text": "in early childhood programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59598.0,
      "end_time": 63121.0,
      "text": "we need to interest state governments in this."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63121.0,
      "end_time": 65347.0,
      "text": "The federal government has a lot on its plate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65346.0,
      "end_time": 67845.0,
      "text": "and state governments are going to have to step up."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67845.0,
      "end_time": 70270.0,
      "text": "So we have to appeal to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70280.0,
      "end_time": 72581.0,
      "text": "the legislators in the state government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72581.0,
      "end_time": 74571.0,
      "text": "and turn to something they understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74571.0,
      "end_time": 76869.0,
      "text": "that they have to promote the economic development"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76869.0,
      "end_time": 78556.0,
      "text": "of their state economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 78556.0,
      "end_time": 80372.0,
      "text": "Now, by promoting economic development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80372.0,
      "end_time": 82860.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mean anything magical."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 82860.0,
      "end_time": 85548.0,
      "text": "All I mean is, is that early childhood education"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85549.0,
      "end_time": 89452.0,
      "text": "can bring more and better jobs to a state"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89452.0,
      "end_time": 92630.0,
      "text": "and can thereby promote higher per capita earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 92630.0,
      "end_time": 94580.0,
      "text": "for the state&#39;s residents."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 94580.0,
      "end_time": 98573.0,
      "text": "Now, I think it&#39;s fair to say that when people think about"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98573.0,
      "end_time": 100577.0,
      "text": "state and local economic development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100577.0,
      "end_time": 104359.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t generally think first about what they&#39;re doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 104359.0,
      "end_time": 106914.0,
      "text": "about childcare and early childhood programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 106914.0,
      "end_time": 110817.0,
      "text": "I know this. I&#39;ve spent most of my career researching these programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110817.0,
      "end_time": 112440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve talked to a lot of directors"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112440.0,
      "end_time": 114768.0,
      "text": "of state economic development agencies about these issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114768.0,
      "end_time": 117310.0,
      "text": "a lot of legislators about these issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117310.0,
      "end_time": 120369.0,
      "text": "When legislators and others think about economic development,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120369.0,
      "end_time": 123625.0,
      "text": "what they first of all think about are business tax incentives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123625.0,
      "end_time": 126503.0,
      "text": "property tax abatements, job creation tax credits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126503.0,
      "end_time": 129190.0,
      "text": "you know, there are a million of these programs all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129190.0,
      "end_time": 131796.0,
      "text": "So for example, states compete very vigorously"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131796.0,
      "end_time": 135460.0,
      "text": "to attract new auto plants or expanded auto plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135461.0,
      "end_time": 137601.0,
      "text": "They hand out all kinds of business tax breaks."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137601.0,
      "end_time": 139799.0,
      "text": "Now, those programs can make sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139799.0,
      "end_time": 142801.0,
      "text": "if they in fact induce new location decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142801.0,
      "end_time": 144185.0,
      "text": "and the way they can make sense is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 144186.0,
      "end_time": 146499.0,
      "text": "by creating more and better jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 146499.0,
      "end_time": 150820.0,
      "text": "they raise employment rates, raise per capita earnings of state residents."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 150820.0,
      "end_time": 152152.0,
      "text": "So there is a benefit to state residents"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 152152.0,
      "end_time": 154301.0,
      "text": "that corresponds to the costs that they&#39;re paying"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 154301.0,
      "end_time": 156573.0,
      "text": "by paying for these business tax breaks."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156574.0,
      "end_time": 160382.0,
      "text": "My argument is essentially that early childhood programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 160382.0,
      "end_time": 164107.0,
      "text": "can do exactly the same thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164107.0,
      "end_time": 168160.0,
      "text": "create more and better jobs, but in a different way."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 170434.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a somewhat more indirect way."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170434.0,
      "end_time": 174790.0,
      "text": "These programs can promote more and better jobs by,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 174800.0,
      "end_time": 176955.0,
      "text": "you build it, you invest in high-quality preschool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 176955.0,
      "end_time": 180773.0,
      "text": "it develops the skills of your local workforce"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 180773.0,
      "end_time": 184516.0,
      "text": "if enough of them stick around, and, in turn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184516.0,
      "end_time": 186668.0,
      "text": "that higher-quality local workforce"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 186669.0,
      "end_time": 191361.0,
      "text": "will be a key driver of creating jobs and creating"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191361.0,
      "end_time": 193869.0,
      "text": "higher earnings per capita in the local community."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193869.0,
      "end_time": 196833.0,
      "text": "Now, let me turn to some numbers on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196833.0,
      "end_time": 201416.0,
      "text": "Okay. If you look at the research evidence --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201416.0,
      "end_time": 206790.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s extensive -- on how much early childhood programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 206790.0,
      "end_time": 210676.0,
      "text": "affect the educational attainment, wages and skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 210676.0,
      "end_time": 214184.0,
      "text": "of former participants in preschool as adults,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 214185.0,
      "end_time": 216821.0,
      "text": "you take those known effects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216821.0,
      "end_time": 219509.0,
      "text": "you take how many of those folks will be expected"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 219509.0,
      "end_time": 223209.0,
      "text": "to stick around the state or local economy and not move out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 223210.0,
      "end_time": 227300.0,
      "text": "and you take research on how much skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 227300.0,
      "end_time": 230201.0,
      "text": "drive job creation, you will conclude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 230201.0,
      "end_time": 232244.0,
      "text": "from these three separate lines of research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232244.0,
      "end_time": 236323.0,
      "text": "that for every dollar invested in early childhood programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 236323.0,
      "end_time": 239776.0,
      "text": "the per capita earnings of state residents"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 239776.0,
      "end_time": 242542.0,
      "text": "go up by two dollars and 78 cents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 242542.0,
      "end_time": 244409.0,
      "text": "so that&#39;s a three-to-one return."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 244409.0,
      "end_time": 247441.0,
      "text": "Now you can get much higher returns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 247442.0,
      "end_time": 251516.0,
      "text": "of up to 16-to-one, if you include anti-crime benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 251516.0,
      "end_time": 256230.0,
      "text": "if you include benefits to former preschool participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 256230.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258414.00000000003,
      "text": "who move to some other state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 258414.0,
      "end_time": 261425.0,
      "text": "but there&#39;s a good reason for focusing on these three dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 261425.0,
      "end_time": 263512.0,
      "text": "because this is salient and important"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 263512.0,
      "end_time": 265802.0,
      "text": "to state legislators and state policy makers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 265802.0,
      "end_time": 267946.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the states that are going to have to act."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 267946.0,
      "end_time": 271245.0,
      "text": "So there is this key benefit that is relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 271245.0,
      "end_time": 274494.0,
      "text": "to state policy makers in terms of economic development."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 274494.0,
      "end_time": 277912.0,
      "text": "Now, one objection you often hear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 277912.0,
      "end_time": 282808.0,
      "text": "or maybe you don&#39;t hear it because people are too polite to say it, is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 282809.0,
      "end_time": 287272.0,
      "text": "why should I pay more taxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 287272.0,
      "end_time": 291550.0,
      "text": "to invest in other people&#39;s children?"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 291550.0,
      "end_time": 294440.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s in it for me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 294440.0,
      "end_time": 296323.0,
      "text": "And the trouble with that objection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 296323.0,
      "end_time": 300325.0,
      "text": "it reflects a total misunderstanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 300325.0,
      "end_time": 303342.0,
      "text": "of how much local economies"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 303342.0,
      "end_time": 306847.0,
      "text": "involve everyone being interdependent."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 306848.0,
      "end_time": 310765.0,
      "text": "Specifically, the interdependency here is, is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 310765.0,
      "end_time": 314298.0,
      "text": "there are huge spillovers of skills --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 314298.0,
      "end_time": 319618.0,
      "text": "that when other people&#39;s children get more skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 319618.0,
      "end_time": 323387.0,
      "text": "that actually increases the prosperity of everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 323387.0,
      "end_time": 326741.0,
      "text": "including people whose skills don&#39;t change."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 326741.0,
      "end_time": 329145.0,
      "text": "So for example, numerous research studies have shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 329145.0,
      "end_time": 331724.0,
      "text": "if you look at what really drives"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 331724.0,
      "end_time": 334188.0,
      "text": "the growth rate of metropolitan areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 334188.0,
      "end_time": 339858.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not so much low taxes, low cost, low wages;"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 339858.0,
      "end_time": 343481.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the skills of the area. Particularly, the proxy for skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 343481.0,
      "end_time": 347160.0,
      "text": "that people use is percentage of college graduates in the area."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 347160.0,
      "end_time": 350950.0,
      "text": "So when you look, for example, at metropolitan areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 350950.0,
      "end_time": 353608.0,
      "text": "such as the Boston area, Minneapolis-St. Paul,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 353608.0,
      "end_time": 358944.0,
      "text": "Silicon Valley, these areas are not doing well economically"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 358944.0,
      "end_time": 361253.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re low-cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 361253.0,
      "end_time": 363178.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if you ever tried to buy a house in Silicon Valley."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 363178.0,
      "end_time": 365995.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not exactly a low-cost proposition."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 365995.0,
      "end_time": 371940.0,
      "text": "They are growing because they have high levels of skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 371940.0,
      "end_time": 375940.0,
      "text": "So when we invest in other people&#39;s children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 375950.0,
      "end_time": 379280.0,
      "text": "and build up those skills, we increase the overall job growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 379280.0,
      "end_time": 380801.0,
      "text": "of a metro area."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 380801.0,
      "end_time": 384688.0,
      "text": "As another example, if we look"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 384689.0,
      "end_time": 387924.0,
      "text": "at what determines an individual&#39;s wages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 387924.0,
      "end_time": 392149.0,
      "text": "and we do statistical exploration of that, what determines wages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 392149.0,
      "end_time": 396672.0,
      "text": "we know that the individual&#39;s wages will depend, in part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 396672.0,
      "end_time": 399103.0,
      "text": "on that individual&#39;s education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 399103.0,
      "end_time": 402960.0,
      "text": "for example whether or not they have a college degree."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 402960.0,
      "end_time": 405434.0,
      "text": "One of the very interesting facts is that, in addition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 405434.0,
      "end_time": 409481.0,
      "text": "we find that even once we hold constant, statistically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 409481.0,
      "end_time": 412385.0,
      "text": "the effect of your own education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 412385.0,
      "end_time": 415585.0,
      "text": "the education of everyone else in your metropolitan area"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 415585.0,
      "end_time": 417556.0,
      "text": "also affects your wages."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 417557.0,
      "end_time": 421761.0,
      "text": "So specifically, if you hold constant your education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 421761.0,
      "end_time": 425864.0,
      "text": "you stick in percentage of college graduates in your metro area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 425864.0,
      "end_time": 429823.0,
      "text": "you will find that has a significant positive effect on your wages"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 429824.0,
      "end_time": 433294.0,
      "text": "without changing your education at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 433294.0,
      "end_time": 436445.0,
      "text": "In fact, this effect is so strong"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 436445.0,
      "end_time": 440258.0,
      "text": "that when someone gets a college degree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 440258.0,
      "end_time": 442698.0,
      "text": "the spillover effects of this on the wages"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 442699.0,
      "end_time": 444592.0,
      "text": "of others in the metropolitan area"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 444592.0,
      "end_time": 447693.0,
      "text": "are actually greater than the direct effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 447694.0,
      "end_time": 451147.0,
      "text": "So if someone gets a college degree, their lifetime earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 451147.0,
      "end_time": 454462.0,
      "text": "go up by a huge amount, over 700,000 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 454462.0,
      "end_time": 456977.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an effect on everyone else in the metro area"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 456977.0,
      "end_time": 460840.0,
      "text": "of driving up the percentage of college graduates in the metro area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 460840.0,
      "end_time": 464256.0,
      "text": "and if you add that up -- it&#39;s a small effect for each person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 464256.0,
      "end_time": 467688.0,
      "text": "but if you add that up across all the people in the metro area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 467688.0,
      "end_time": 471313.0,
      "text": "you actually get that the increase in wages for everyone else"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 471314.0,
      "end_time": 474227.0,
      "text": "in the metropolitan area adds up to almost a million dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 474227.0,
      "end_time": 476304.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s actually greater than the direct benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 476305.0,
      "end_time": 479359.0,
      "text": "of the person choosing to get education."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 479359.0,
      "end_time": 480717.0,
      "text": "Now, what&#39;s going on here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 480718.0,
      "end_time": 484641.0,
      "text": "What can explain these huge spillover effects of education?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 484641.0,
      "end_time": 486115.0,
      "text": "Well, let&#39;s think about it this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 486115.0,
      "end_time": 489438.0,
      "text": "I can be the most skilled person in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 489438.0,
      "end_time": 493239.0,
      "text": "but if everyone else at my firm lacks skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 493239.0,
      "end_time": 496207.0,
      "text": "my employer is going to find it more difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 496208.0,
      "end_time": 500264.0,
      "text": "to introduce new technology, new production techniques."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 500264.0,
      "end_time": 503866.0,
      "text": "So as a result, my employer is going to be less productive."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 503866.0,
      "end_time": 507467.0,
      "text": "They will not be able to afford to pay me as good wages."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 507467.0,
      "end_time": 511147.0,
      "text": "Even if everyone at my firm has good skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511148.0,
      "end_time": 514656.0,
      "text": "if the workers at the suppliers to my firm"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 514655.0,
      "end_time": 516626.0,
      "text": "do not have good skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 516626.0,
      "end_time": 519230.0,
      "text": "my firm is going to be less competitive"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 519230.0,
      "end_time": 521408.0,
      "text": "competing in national and international markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 521408.0,
      "end_time": 524502.0,
      "text": "And again, the firm that&#39;s less competitive"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 524502.0,
      "end_time": 527190.0,
      "text": "will not be able to pay as good wages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 527191.0,
      "end_time": 531324.0,
      "text": "and then, particularly in high-tech businesses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 531324.0,
      "end_time": 534584.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re constantly stealing ideas and workers from other businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 534585.0,
      "end_time": 537805.0,
      "text": "So clearly the productivity of firms in Silicon Valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 537805.0,
      "end_time": 541599.0,
      "text": "has a lot to do with the skills not only of the workers at their firm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 541600.0,
      "end_time": 546190.0,
      "text": "but the workers at all the other firms in the metro area."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 546190.0,
      "end_time": 549553.0,
      "text": "So as a result, if we can invest in other people&#39;s children"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 549553.0,
      "end_time": 551955.0,
      "text": "through preschool and other early childhood programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 551955.0,
      "end_time": 555611.0,
      "text": "that are high-quality, we not only help those children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 555611.0,
      "end_time": 559232.0,
      "text": "we help everyone in the metropolitan area"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 559232.0,
      "end_time": 562903.0,
      "text": "gain in wages and we&#39;ll have the metropolitan area"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 562903.0,
      "end_time": 564925.0,
      "text": "gain in job growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 564925.0,
      "end_time": 567455.0,
      "text": "Another objection used sometimes here"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 567456.0,
      "end_time": 569684.0,
      "text": "to invest in early childhood programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 569684.0,
      "end_time": 573405.0,
      "text": "is concern about people moving out."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 573405.0,
      "end_time": 577640.0,
      "text": "So, you know, maybe Ohio&#39;s thinking about investing"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 577640.0,
      "end_time": 579884.0,
      "text": "in more preschool education"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 579884.0,
      "end_time": 583694.0,
      "text": "for children in Columbus, Ohio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 583694.0,
      "end_time": 585953.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re worried that these little Buckeyes will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 585953.0,
      "end_time": 588870.0,
      "text": "for some strange reason, decide to move to Ann Arbor, Michigan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 588870.0,
      "end_time": 590387.0,
      "text": "and become Wolverines."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 590387.0,
      "end_time": 593680.0,
      "text": "And maybe Michigan will be thinking about investing"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 593681.0,
      "end_time": 596122.0,
      "text": "in preschool in Ann Arbor, Michigan, and be worried"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 596122.0,
      "end_time": 599357.0,
      "text": "these little Wolverines will end up moving to Ohio and becoming Buckeyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 599357.0,
      "end_time": 603348.0,
      "text": "And so they&#39;ll both underinvest because everyone&#39;s going to move out."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 603349.0,
      "end_time": 606290.0,
      "text": "Well, the reality is, if you look at the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 606290.0,
      "end_time": 610502.0,
      "text": "Americans aren&#39;t as hyper-mobile as people sometimes assume."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 610503.0,
      "end_time": 615623.0,
      "text": "The data is that over 60 percent of Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 615623.0,
      "end_time": 618610.0,
      "text": "spend most of their working careers"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 618610.0,
      "end_time": 621831.0,
      "text": "in the state they were born in, over 60 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 621831.0,
      "end_time": 625926.0,
      "text": "That percentage does not vary much from state to state."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 625926.0,
      "end_time": 629300.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t vary much with the state&#39;s economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 629300.0,
      "end_time": 630828.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s depressed or booming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 630828.0,
      "end_time": 633149.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t vary much over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 633149.0,
      "end_time": 638962.0,
      "text": "So the reality is, if you invest in kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 638962.0,
      "end_time": 641461.0,
      "text": "they will stay."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 641461.0,
      "end_time": 644499.0,
      "text": "Or at least, enough of them will stay"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 644499.0,
      "end_time": 647920.0,
      "text": "that it will pay off for your state economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 647920.0,
      "end_time": 651843.0,
      "text": "Okay, so to sum up, there is a lot of research evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 651844.0,
      "end_time": 654998.0,
      "text": "that early childhood programs, if run in a high-quality way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 654998.0,
      "end_time": 657854.0,
      "text": "pay off in higher adult skills."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 657854.0,
      "end_time": 659421.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of research evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 659421.0,
      "end_time": 663450.0,
      "text": "that those folks will stick around the state economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 663450.0,
      "end_time": 666362.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s a lot of evidence that having more workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 666362.0,
      "end_time": 668452.0,
      "text": "with higher skills in your local economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 668452.0,
      "end_time": 672131.0,
      "text": "pays off in higher wages and job growth for your local economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 672131.0,
      "end_time": 675574.0,
      "text": "and if you calculate the numbers for each dollar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 675574.0,
      "end_time": 678303.0,
      "text": "we get about three dollars back"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 678303.0,
      "end_time": 680478.0,
      "text": "in benefits for the state economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 680478.0,
      "end_time": 684890.0,
      "text": "So in my opinion, the research evidence is compelling"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 684900.0,
      "end_time": 686914.0,
      "text": "and the logic of this is compelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 686914.0,
      "end_time": 690604.0,
      "text": "So what are the barriers to getting it done?"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 690604.0,
      "end_time": 693868.0,
      "text": "Well, one obvious barrier is cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 693868.0,
      "end_time": 698198.0,
      "text": "So if you look at what it would cost"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 698198.0,
      "end_time": 701250.0,
      "text": "if every state government invested"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 701250.0,
      "end_time": 705230.0,
      "text": "in universal preschool at age four, full-day preschool at age four,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 705230.0,
      "end_time": 708645.0,
      "text": "the total annual national cost would be roughly"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 708645.0,
      "end_time": 710949.0,
      "text": "30 billion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 710950.0,
      "end_time": 713375.0,
      "text": "So, 30 billion dollars is a lot of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 713375.0,
      "end_time": 717120.0,
      "text": "On the other hand, if you reflect on"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 717120.0,
      "end_time": 720980.0,
      "text": "that the U.S.&#39;s population is over 300 million,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 720980.0,
      "end_time": 723663.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re talking about an amount of money"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 723663.0,
      "end_time": 726283.0,
      "text": "that amounts to 100 dollars per capita."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 726283.0,
      "end_time": 729261.0,
      "text": "Okay? A hundred dollars per capita, per person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 729261.0,
      "end_time": 733266.0,
      "text": "is something that any state government can afford to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 733266.0,
      "end_time": 738150.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just a simple matter of political will to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 738150.0,
      "end_time": 739895.0,
      "text": "And, of course, as I mentioned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 739895.0,
      "end_time": 742490.0,
      "text": "this cost has corresponding benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 742490.0,
      "end_time": 744225.0,
      "text": "I mentioned there&#39;s a multiplier of about three,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 744225.0,
      "end_time": 746325.0,
      "text": "2.78, for the state economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 746325.0,
      "end_time": 749354.0,
      "text": "in terms of over 80 billion in extra earnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 749354.0,
      "end_time": 752378.0,
      "text": "And if we want to translate that from just billions of dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 752378.0,
      "end_time": 754271.0,
      "text": "to something that might mean something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 754271.0,
      "end_time": 757858.0,
      "text": "what we&#39;re talking about is that, for the average low-income kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 757859.0,
      "end_time": 760976.0,
      "text": "that would increase earnings by about 10 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 760976.0,
      "end_time": 764175.0,
      "text": "over their whole career, just doing the preschool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 764175.0,
      "end_time": 766689.0,
      "text": "not improving K-12 or anything else after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 766690.0,
      "end_time": 769238.0,
      "text": "not doing anything with college tuition or access,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 769238.0,
      "end_time": 771934.0,
      "text": "just directly improving preschool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 771934.0,
      "end_time": 774233.0,
      "text": "and we would get five percent higher earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 774233.0,
      "end_time": 775628.0,
      "text": "for middle-class kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 775629.0,
      "end_time": 777694.0,
      "text": "So this is an investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 777694.0,
      "end_time": 780602.0,
      "text": "that pays off in very concrete terms"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 780602.0,
      "end_time": 785210.0,
      "text": "for a broad range of income groups in the state&#39;s population"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 785220.0,
      "end_time": 789532.0,
      "text": "and produces large and tangible benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 789532.0,
      "end_time": 792860.0,
      "text": "Now, that&#39;s one barrier."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 792860.0,
      "end_time": 795508.0,
      "text": "I actually think the more profound barrier"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 795508.0,
      "end_time": 799938.0,
      "text": "is the long-term nature of the benefits from early childhood programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 799938.0,
      "end_time": 802784.0,
      "text": "So the argument I&#39;m making is, is that we&#39;re increasing"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 802784.0,
      "end_time": 804539.0,
      "text": "the quality of our local workforce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 804539.0,
      "end_time": 807205.0,
      "text": "and thereby increasing economic development."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 807205.0,
      "end_time": 810585.0,
      "text": "Obviously if we have a preschool with four-year-olds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 810585.0,
      "end_time": 812953.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not sending these kids out at age five"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 812953.0,
      "end_time": 816468.0,
      "text": "to work in the sweatshops, right? At least I hope not."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 816468.0,
      "end_time": 819880.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re talking about an investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 819880.0,
      "end_time": 822350.0,
      "text": "that in terms of impacts on the state economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 822350.0,
      "end_time": 826311.0,
      "text": "is not going to really pay off for 15 or 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 826311.0,
      "end_time": 829169.0,
      "text": "and of course America is notorious for being"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 829169.0,
      "end_time": 832175.0,
      "text": "a short term-oriented society."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 832176.0,
      "end_time": 833836.0,
      "text": "Now one response you can make to this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 833836.0,
      "end_time": 835361.0,
      "text": "and I sometimes have done this in talks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 835361.0,
      "end_time": 838438.0,
      "text": "is people can talk about, there are benefits for these programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 838438.0,
      "end_time": 842850.0,
      "text": "in reducing special ed and remedial education costs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 842850.0,
      "end_time": 844391.0,
      "text": "there are benefits, parents care about preschool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 844391.0,
      "end_time": 846641.0,
      "text": "maybe we&#39;ll get some migration effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 846641.0,
      "end_time": 848959.0,
      "text": "from parents seeking good preschool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 848959.0,
      "end_time": 850606.0,
      "text": "and I think those are true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 850606.0,
      "end_time": 852768.0,
      "text": "but in some sense they&#39;re missing the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 852768.0,
      "end_time": 855339.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, this is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 855339.0,
      "end_time": 859264.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re investing in now for the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 859264.0,
      "end_time": 863213.0,
      "text": "And so what I want to leave you with is"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 863213.0,
      "end_time": 865519.0,
      "text": "what I think is the ultimate question."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 865519.0,
      "end_time": 868353.0,
      "text": "I mean, I&#39;m an economist, but this is ultimately"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 868353.0,
      "end_time": 873897.0,
      "text": "not an economic question, it&#39;s a moral question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 873898.0,
      "end_time": 878105.0,
      "text": "Are we willing, as Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 878105.0,
      "end_time": 881555.0,
      "text": "are we as a society still capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 881555.0,
      "end_time": 886339.0,
      "text": "of making the political choice to sacrifice now"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 886339.0,
      "end_time": 888988.0,
      "text": "by paying more taxes"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 888988.0,
      "end_time": 894193.0,
      "text": "in order to improve the long-term future"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 894193.0,
      "end_time": 897610.0,
      "text": "of not only our kids, but our community?"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 897610.0,
      "end_time": 902570.0,
      "text": "Are we still capable of that as a country?"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 902570.0,
      "end_time": 904498.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s something that each and every citizen"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 904498.0,
      "end_time": 907410.0,
      "text": "and voter needs to ask themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 907410.0,
      "end_time": 909986.0,
      "text": "Is that something that you are still invested in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 909986.0,
      "end_time": 912720.0,
      "text": "that you still believe in the notion of investment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 912720.0,
      "end_time": 914119.0,
      "text": "That is the notion of investment."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 914119.0,
      "end_time": 916693.0,
      "text": "You sacrifice now for a return later."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 916693.0,
      "end_time": 920331.0,
      "text": "So I think the research evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 920331.0,
      "end_time": 922969.0,
      "text": "on the benefits of early childhood programs"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 922969.0,
      "end_time": 926576.0,
      "text": "for the local economy is extremely strong."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 926576.0,
      "end_time": 930858.0,
      "text": "However, the moral and political choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 930858.0,
      "end_time": 935962.0,
      "text": "is still up to us, as citizens and as voters."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 935962.0,
      "end_time": 939985.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}